        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3781",
        "content": "In what ways did his father show his favoritism towards Joseph? The Hebrew word rendered in the older translations, \"coat of many colors,\" means literally, \"long sleeved tunic.\"",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
