        "speaker_id": "LibriTTS_R-3781",
        "content": "Soon through his activities these almost instinctive habits, guided by rules, assume the nature of customs that have a sanction, often of religion, practically always of enforcement through the patriarch.",
        "style_prompt": "F_p-high_s-slow_e-normal",
        "gender": "F",
